head_commit.message:
VPN-3508 - part 8 - URLOpener as shared component (#5289)

In this PR we also have:
- remove __VPN_GRAPHICSAPI__ param: nobody uses it and it introduces an extra
  dep for MozillaVPN
- register the list of custom label-urls in MozillaVPN
- more unit-tests
